name: Babyzoro Inu
description: Babyzoro Inu is a community controlled deflationary token, Babyzoro Inu's purpose is to develop solutions that will make the cryptocurrency space safer and easier to understand for everyone.And then we will donate 1% to charity for poor children and people in need. The deflationary mechanism of the Babyzoro Inu token includes a redistribution system. 3% of each transaction is distributed as a reward to holders. On top of this, 40% of the total $BabyZORO supply will be burned
